messages.content: What type of image does comfyui-load-image-39 node load?
The node loads PNG images sequentially with metadata.
Is comfyui-load-image-39 node compatible with all PNG images?
No, it is only supported for PNG images that have been created by ComfyUI.
How can I add the comfyui-load-image-39 node?
You can add the node by selecting 'Add node > image > Load Image #39'.
What update was made in version 1.0.1?
In version 1.0.1, the node was updated to reset the index when it reached the end of the file, and to fix a conversion from primitive string to CLIP Text Encord (Prompt).
